{"tid":1602824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［和理非入］其實你地可以做得更多","createTime":"2019-09-29T14:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T16:42:23.000Z","uid":166637,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8d6ae4058a2b94ddad8dc2a170bdf768c665e492","tid":1602824,"uid":166637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"好多人聲稱自己係和理非<br />\n睇到新聞好嬲<br />\n但我叫佢地開個twitter都難<br />\n自從無咗民陣遊行 <br />\n有d和理非仲未搵到自己定位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔好覺得 我唔做都有人做架啦</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n係唔會架<br />\n<br />\ntwitter戰輸撚晒啦屌<br />\n每月兌美金<br />\n罷搭黨鐵罷食罷買藍店<br />\n俾錢印文宣貼牆<br />\n每日一twitt<br />\nn個like 同retweet 幫推有用twitt上熱門<br />\n以下係參考:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WgGoMT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WgGoMT.jpg&h=161bca92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請你地記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>勝利唔係從天而降<br />\n勿以善小而不為</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有d和理非唔知自己出去有咩做<br />\n人鏈，物資補給，哨兵，街坊屌狗，衣服提供<br />\n喺手足做緊野時開遮，幫手搵記者，影低狗罪行，整banner俾傳媒影相等等<br />\n都係你可以做！<br />\n<br />\n我衷心希望 當前線為我地擋子彈時<br />\n你地要記得<br />\n清楚喺後勤既工作<br />\n另外 無gear既請唔好留太夜<br />\n前線手足會為你地set roadblock<br />\n尤其女仔 唔好要手足太擔心<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKop53f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKop53f.jpg&h=842b1451&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cae6f7754f962a87e8af524219dc31483bf8c597","tid":1602824,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:03:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91742d9fdaabac3d78a351e775ed8c623bfc2619","tid":1602824,"uid":311907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"大家係咪唔記得好多野要繼續做？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a hr